      <title>红海扰乱导致油轮运价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/fuel-tanker-rates-are-soaring-on-red-sea-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对红海航运的袭击波及全球市场，在主要贸易路线上运输燃料的成本正在飙升。]]></description>
